modName: Elaborate Dragonsting Dagger and Sword Retex for Jaysus Swor
summary: A retex of the new dragonsting dagger and sword from jaysus
descriptionHtml:
This Is Now Outdated All Jaysus Retextures Moved To ; http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4871

This is retex that adds gold gilding to the blood grooves of the dragonsting dagger and sword as well as maing the ornaments gold and changing the wood to a more regal looking redwood.

There are three versions of this mod so far;

The Redwood (redwood scabbard and handle with gold inlay all along)

The Ebony wood (Ebony wood scabbard and handle with gold inlay all along)

The Dark Crusader ( Dark Metal akin to ebony with a dark wood scabbard and handle and gold inlay all along)

You MUST have the mod Jaysus Swords to use this; http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1002

Feedback would be much appreciated as this is my first mod :) and if you like, Endorse!

i hope you guys enjoy this i will add a few different versions with various colours, first up is the redwood version and the ebony should be up in the next few minutes.

if you want to change this then ask jaysus its his models and original textures all ive done is tweak it to my liking, and yes i do have jaysus\'s permission to retexture his mods :)
